latest_release_info.name: Unchained-Mods
latest_release_info.description: Mod Loading Framework and default mods

info.name: Unchained-Mods
info.description: Mod Loading Framework and default mods

releases.release_notes_markdown:
## UI:
- shorter mod loading notifications
- pause menu UI expanded vertically
- ListPlayers button added to pause menu
## Unchained Multiplayer:
- FPSSync mod re-enabled (matches client and server FPS)
   - feedback is welcome
## Offline Play:
- "Map Selector" mod
  - Both main menu (planet icon) and in pause menu
-  "Mod Menu" mod
   - Mouse input: toggle with F3
   - Numpad: Hold Num0, Use Num1-9 to select option. Use Num+/Num- to switch category
- Better bots (normal + playerbots):
  - enabled by default
  - shorter reaction time
  - will feint occasionally
